{"tid":1574611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★這次微軟的bug，讓你網都上不了! 請勿更新KB4515384","createTime":"2019-09-16T13:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:14:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"904c76851079b508f41bc5063284c6deedf89b12","tid":1574611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.zi.org.tw/dacota/2019/09/16124308/1568608987-6536677be2df4d1a654797c6da8fee96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.zi.org.tw%2Fdacota%2F2019%2F09%2F16124308%2F1568608987-6536677be2df4d1a654797c6da8fee96.jpg&h=e89a8d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前陣子微軟的更新檔 KB4515384推出，本來是為了解決 Cortana 程序佔用到40%以上的問題<br />\n<br />\n同時也對其他不明顯的坑進行修補。<br />\n<br />\n不過，微軟好像填了一個坑，卻挖下一個更深的坑。<br />\n<br />\n在更新最新版本之後，微軟表示這一更新將會導致&ldquo;開始&rdquo;選單以及 Windows 10 搜尋出現錯誤<br />\n<br />\n同時，音訊也會出現一點小問題，更為嚴重的是 KB4515384 還會導致網路卡停止工作的問題，也就是說不能上網。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/19/09/kb4515384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F19%2F09%2Fkb4515384.jpg&h=2e818e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在微軟社區、Reddit 以及 Feedback Hub 上，有不少用戶在抱怨更新 KB4515384 之後，導致網卡停止工作<br />\n<br />\n就連禁用網路以及 WiFi 都會出現 bug。<br />\n<br />\n根據網友的回應內容，該更新導致的網路問題並不能通過重新安裝網路卡驅動來解決<br />\n<br />\n想要解決這個問題，現階段只能回到上一個版本<br />\n<br />\n不然就要等微軟推送修復更新<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://dacota.tw/blog/post/kb4515384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdacota.tw%2Fblog%2Fpost%2Fkb4515384&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=1381ba5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dacota.tw/blog/post/kb4515384</a>"},{"pid":"c5cbc6922bfb013701d0ea147e550b5ae6802edb","tid":1574611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shockin